'''Agent Jones''' is an immigration agent who came to deport [[Esau Ajawke]].

==History==
When Immigration found out [[Esau Ajawke]] had tuberculosis, they came to the hospital to start the deportation process. Sam lied and said that Esau's condition had worsened to buy him enough time for him to meet his son before they took him away.

==Career==
He works for Immigration and Customs Enforcement.
